Interface OrderedListADT<T>

All Known Implementing Classes:
OrderedList
public interface OrderedListADT<T>
extends ListADT<T>

The OrderedListADT interface extends the ListADT by providing a method to add elements to the list in an ordered fashion. The ordering of elements is determined by the template type T, which much implement the Comparable interface from the Java API.
